8
00:00:18.150 --> 00:00:20.160
served by those organizations.

9
00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:22.800
These concepts are
key considerations

10
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:25.390
when thinking about having
a security mindset.

11
00:00:25.390 --> 00:00:28.519
You'll have to recognize not
only what you're defending,

12
00:00:28.519 --> 00:00:31.345
but what or who you're
defending against.

13
00:00:32.345 --> 00:00:33.380
For example, it's important to

14
00:00:33.380 --> 00:00:35.630
recognize the types
of assets that are

15
00:00:35.630 --> 00:00:36.770
essential to maintaining

16
00:00:36.770 --> 00:00:38.825
an organization's
business functions,

17
00:00:38.825 --> 00:00:41.135
along with types of threats,

18
00:00:41.135 --> 00:00:43.070
risks, and vulnerabilities that

19
00:00:43.070 --> 00:00:45.455
can negatively
impact those assets.

20
00:00:45.455 --> 00:00:48.845
And that's what having a security
mindset is all about.

21
00:00:48.845 --> 00:00:51.380
A security mindset
is the ability

22
00:00:51.380 --> 00:00:53.510
to evaluate risk and constantly

23
00:00:53.510 --> 00:00:54.920
seek out and identify

24
00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:58.235
the potential or actual
breach of a system,

25
00:00:58.235 --> 00:01:00.235
application, or data.

26
00:01:01.235 --> 00:01:01.820
Earlier in the program,

27
00:01:01.820 --> 00:01:03.950
we discussed threats, risks,

28
00:01:03.950 --> 00:01:05.930
and vulnerabilities
that are posed by

29
00:01:05.930 --> 00:01:09.025
social engineering
attacks, such as phishing.

30
00:01:09.025 --> 00:01:11.390
These attacks are
designed to compromise

31
00:01:11.390 --> 00:01:13.910
an organization's assets to help

32
00:01:13.910 --> 00:01:15.545
the threat actor or actors gain

33
00:01:15.545 --> 00:01:17.825
access to sensitive information.

34
00:01:17.825 --> 00:01:19.940
Using our security mindset can

35
00:01:19.940 --> 00:01:22.250
help prevent these
types of attacks.

36
00:01:22.250 --> 00:01:24.905
It's important that
we're constantly staying

37
00:01:24.905 --> 00:01:27.980
up-to-date with the kinds of attacks
that are happening.

