the latest security threats
or vulnerabilities.

41
00:01:35.855 --> 00:01:38.210
As you do this, new ideas for

42
00:01:38.210 --> 00:01:40.880
protecting company
data may come to mind.

43
00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:43.190
Security is an
everyday objective

44
00:01:43.190 --> 00:01:45.610
for every security
team in the industry.

45
00:01:45.610 --> 00:01:48.050
So having a security
mindset helps analysts

46
00:01:48.050 --> 00:01:50.675
defend against the constant
pressure from attackers.

47
