00:02:10.910 --> 00:02:14.480
high-importance assets, such
as intellectual property,

55
00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:19.205
trade secrets, PII, and
even financial information.

56
00:02:19.205 --> 00:02:21.590
Your security mindset
allows you to

57
00:02:21.590 --> 00:02:23.930
